info.title: Always Something There To Remind Me

metadata.album: Promises, Promises: The Very Best of Naked Eyes

lines.text: i walk along the city streets
you used to walk along with me
i was born to love her
and i will never be free
you'll always be a part of me
if you should find you miss the sweet
and tender love we used to share
just come back to the places
i was born to love her
and i will never be free
you'll always be a part of me

paragraphs.text: i walk along the city streets you used to walk along with me and every step i take reminds me of just how we used to be
well how can i forget you girl when there is always something there to remind me? always something there to remind me
